Join the Conversation To find out more about Facebook commenting please read the Conversation Guidelines and FAQs PODCAST: Hawk Central tackles 5-0 Iowa's ways to improve Hawk Central staff 9:19 p.m. CDT October 7, 2015 Hawk Central CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
Last week's Wisconsin win was the ideal type of victory for coach Kirk Ferentz. It was a win with plenty of sore spots. 
C.J. Beathard struggled. So did the offensive line. The defense stepped up time and time again. 
There are points of excellence and plenty of points on which to improve. 
In the latest episode of the "Hawk Central Hour" on KXnO radio, Rick Brown, Chad Leistikow and Ross Peterson break down just how "perfect" Iowa is at 5-0.
